overview: On January 22nd GCW vs New South is live on FITE straight from Singin' River Brewing in Florence, AL. The first matches are already announced, you can check them below:  Sawyer Wreck (GCW) vs Donnie Primetime (New South)  Bussy vs The Carnies  Los Macizos vs Infrared  Tony Deppen vs Brandon Williams  Blake Christian vs Hunter Drake  ... and much more!
title: GCW Vs New South
